 i kaže

1349
00:56:55,500 --> 00:56:57,400
 nastavili su drugim putem.

1350
00:56:57,400 --> 00:56:59,420
 Zavate šta mi to govori?

1351
00:56:59,420 --> 00:57:01,020
 Da nakon susreta s Isusom

1352
00:57:01,020 --> 00:57:01,840
 mi ne možemo nastaviti

1353
00:57:01,840 --> 00:57:02,500
 istim putem.

1354
00:57:05,500 --> 00:57:06,640
 Nakon susreta

1355
00:57:06,640 --> 00:57:07,540
 s Isusom

1356
00:57:07,540 --> 00:57:09,160
 mi nešto moramo promijeniti.

1357
00:57:09,160 --> 00:57:11,340
 Ne mogu ostati isti.

1358
00:57:11,340 --> 00:57:13,240
 Jer ako sam ostao isti

1359
00:57:13,240 --> 00:57:14,520
 a onda ga nisam stvarno susreo.

1360
00:57:14,520 --> 00:57:16,200
 Znate o onom priču

1361
00:57:16,200 --> 00:57:16,860
 o muslimanu

1362
00:57:16,860 --> 00:57:18,040
 koju se u Egiptu obratio

1363
00:57:18,040 --> 00:57:19,340
 i sada je tražio

1364
00:57:19,340 --> 00:57:20,620
 katoličkog svećanika

1365
00:57:20,620 --> 00:57:22,060
 da se krsti.

1366
00:57:22,060 --> 00:57:25,180
 I dolazi do njega

1367
00:57:25,180 --> 00:57:25,440
 i kaže

1368
00:57:25,440 --> 00:57:26,560
 ja bi se želio krstiti

1369
00:57:26,560 --> 00:57:28,100
 jer mu se Isus ukazao.

1370
00:57:28,740 --> 00:57:30,280
 i dolazi da bi se htio krstiti

1371
00:57:30,280 --> 00:57:30,840
 i on mu kaže

1372
00:57:30,840 --> 00:57:32,080
 kao pa ono

1373
00:57:32,080 --> 00:57:33,160
 to je jako opasno

1374
00:57:33,160 --> 00:57:34,560
 pa tvoji te mogu ubiti

1375
00:57:34,560 --> 00:57:35,280
 i stvarno se mogu

1376
00:57:35,280 --> 00:57:36,300
 loše stvari dogoditi.

1377
00:57:36,300 --> 00:57:37,720
 I on ga gleda i kaže

1378
00:57:37,720 --> 00:57:39,280
 a ti ga nisi vidio?

1379
00:57:39,280 --> 00:57:42,780
 Ako ti misliš da me briga

1380
00:57:42,780 --> 00:57:45,560
 šta će mi se dogoditi?

1381
00:57:45,560 --> 00:57:47,680
 A onda ga ti nisi susreo.

1382
00:57:47,680 --> 00:57:49,240
 Ja se želim krstiti.

1383
00:57:49,240 --> 00:57:50,920
 Tako da

1384
00:57:50,920 --> 00:57:52,400
 ako želiš promjenu

1385
00:57:52,400 --> 00:57:53,740
 susretni ga

1386
00:57:53,740 --> 00:57:55,480
 i idi prema tom cilju

1387
00:57:55,480 --> 00:57:56,160
 koji te on zove.

1388
00:57:56,160 --> 00:57:56,540
 Amen.

1389
00:57:58,740 --> 00:58:28,720
 Hvala što pratite kanal.

